$ON_DATREG
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_DATREG From W5CTR4
Return

$AV_DATREG
Chgfmt [M]DATREG(indice) With "DPZ:"+GFMDAT
Gosub _AFF
Return

$ON_DATAVA
